{"parentUuid":"42572d21-e6d3-43a0-a08e-6f5ebda0762b","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"8a0970a7-992a-482d-b1fb-9fa84d4f1b3d","agentId":"a03d1193a3e17de91","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015qfbBbAzBhpFYyMbdLxewo","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Meterly\n2\t\n3\t## Stack\n4\t- Cloud environment: AWS (ECS Fargate + RDS PostgreSQL + ALB), Terraform under infra/\n5\t- Language/runtime: Python 3.12\n6\t- Framework(s): FastAPI\n7\t- Data stores: PostgreSQL\n8\t- Migration tool: Alembic\n9\t- Cloud / IaC: AWS + Terraform\n10\t- Auth provider: API keys (Argon2id-hashed at rest), per-key rate limiting — no third-party IdP.\n11\t  `api_keys.scope` (`'ingest'` default, `'admin'` elevated) gates `PUT /v1/quotas`; provision an\n12\t  admin key with `scripts/seed_api_key.py --admin`.\n13\t- Observability: CloudWatch + X-Ray + Sentry (release-tagged)\n14\t- Packaging / runtime: container (Docker) — justified: deploys through the ECS canary path\n15\t\n16\t## How to run / build / test\n17\t- Start: `uvicorn src.main:app --port 8000` (smoke check expects HTTP 200 at `http://localhost:8000/health`)\n18\t- Test:  `pytest --cov=src --cov-branch`\n19\t- Migrate: `alembic upgrade head` (run before deploying; also run locally after pulling schema changes)\n20\t- Deploy: CI on merge — see docs/pipeline-deployment-targets.md (build-provenance → deploy.yml chain)\n21\t\n22\t## Frontend design source\n23\t- Design source: none (API only)\n24\t\n25\t## Conventions\n26\t- Module layout: src/ package (src/main.py app entry), facade modules per code-standards defaults\n27\t- Test locations: tests/ as test_*.py\n28\t\n29\t## What \"done\" means\n30\t- Smoke check passes, security report clean, tests pass at >= 85% coverage,\n31\t  docs updated for touched directories, PR description written.\n32\t\n33\t<!--\n34\t  REMEMBER per project: the smoke-check.sh hook reads Start/health values above.\n35\t  Set them here, or export SMOKE_START_CMD / SMOKE_HEALTH_URL, or (frontend-only)\n36\t  swap in the build-check variant of smoke-check.sh from the spec.\n37\t-->\n38\t"}]},"uuid":"e23e4c05-ff89-463a-a381-63526aea72a8","timestamp":"2026-07-09T03:58:55.577Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"42572d21-e6d3-43a0-a08e-6f5ebda0762b","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"c:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"d6fd840f-4c15-4ec4-8e2b-f4a42b2cbb1a","version":"2.1.204","gitBranch":"feature/metric-quotas"}
